释义：
keep in mind 铭记于心，记住
前文中提到的 have in mind 表示“在意某事”，而 keep in mind 则表示“铭记于心”，“记住某事”等。可以使用 keep somebody ( something ) in mind 或 keep in mind that 主语+动词的形态。
例句：
Keep in mind that she will never fall in love with you.
记住，她绝对不会喜欢上你的。
Let's keep in mind this is our last chance to do that.
要记住，这是我们最后的机会。
Thanks for coming in. We will definitely keep you in mind.
谢谢你能来。我们肯定会记住你的。
对话：
A: I want to get a new computer.
我想弄台新电脑。
B: Keep in mind that will cost a lot.
要知道肯定要花不少钱。